[270],{"type":191,"value":271},"Prettier 的自动换行策略使代码 diff 变得难以阅读，并且没有选项可以用来关闭 print-width 配置的换行策略。尽管可以通过 ESLint 来纠正 Prettier 的行为，但是这麻烦且降低了性能。所以 antfu 的策略是使用自己配置的整套 ESLint 规则共享包。",{"type":185,"tag":232,"props":273,"children":274},{},[275,276],{"type":191,"value":236},{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":277,"children":280},{"href":278,"rel":279},"https://antfu.me/posts/why-not-prettier-zh",[241],[281],{"type":191,"value":282},"为什么我不使用 Prettier | antfu",{"type":185,"tag":225,"props":284,"children":286},{"id":285},"eslint-only-方案的优势",[287],{"type":191,"value":288},"ESLint-only 方案的优势",{"type":185,"tag":232,"props":290,"children":291},{},[292],{"type":191,"value":293},"使用纯 ESLint 进行代码格式化的优势包括：",{"type":185,"tag":193,"props":295,"children":296},{},[297,302,307,312],{"type":185,"tag":197,"props":298,"children":299},{},[300],{"type":191,"value":301},"统一的配置入口，减少工具链复杂度",{"type":185,"tag":197,"props":303,"children":304},{},[305],{"type":191,"value":306},"更好的性能（无需在 ESLint 和 Prettier 之间来回传递）",{"type":185,"tag":197,"props":308,"children":309},{},[310],{"type":191,"value":311},"更灵活的规则定制能力",{"type":185,"tag":197,"props":313,"children":314},{},[315],{"type":191,"value":316},"更好的编辑器集成体验",{"title":178,"searchDepth":318,"depth":318,"links":319},2,[320,321,322],{"id":188,"depth":318,"text":188},{"id":220,"depth":318,"text":223},{"id":258,"depth":318,"text":258},"markdown","content:6.maps:_workflow:linter:linter.md","content","6.maps/_workflow/linter/linter.md","6.maps/_workflow/linter/linter","md",[330,332],{"_path":203,"title":206,"description":331},"ESLint 是 JavaScript 和 TypeScript 的代码质量检查工具，帮助开发者保持代码风格一致性和减少错误。",{"_path":333,"title":334,"description":335},"/maps/_workflow/monorepo/monorepo","Monorepo","Monorepo 是一种将多个项目放在同一个代码仓库中的管理方式，旨在提高团队协作和代码复用效率",1772504901146]